{"tid":1785694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[12.24討論] 活動太多係好事定壞事？洗唔洗處理下","createTime":"2019-12-16T14:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T15:07:18.000Z","uid":223763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"691d9a740fdd76233e9ea94199d3372162b9eec7","tid":1785694,"uid":223763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"知道大家平安夜趁多人出街想搞集會遊行<br />\n但係而家至少已經有三個活動<br />\n一個遊行 一個和你shop 一個蘭桂坊<br />\n和你shop 都分咗幾區<br />\n<br />\n我知道平安夜經濟攪炒好重要 剩係遊行冇乜用<br />\n但宣傳係一個問題 半年嚟已經証明咗力谷單一活動先會多人 好似12.1尖沙咀遊行宣傳咗4日有38萬人<br />\n定係平安夜大家本身已經會出街 所以分散宣傳都可以？<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ur1is5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fur1is5t.jpg&h=140d5685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDHQ3DQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDHQ3DQ.jpg&h=b4c1b616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nhi,又係小弟呀，1224倒數遊行紙已入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f74b7cd065ebdfedc7e5f4390e56448db749619f","tid":1785694,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2950afd057274565eea26c3b70b05069f4213c22","tid":1785694,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span